Professional Wrestling is alive a well in Portland, OR! The _West Coast Wrestling Connection_ (qv), or The WCWC, brings wrestling Fans old school pro wrestling every Saturday night on KPDX-TV, Oregon. Gandrel, Matt Striker, The Grappler, Eric Right, Ethan HD, Adam Thornstowe, Mikey O'Shea, Sinn Bodhi, The Bonus Boyz, Marcus Malone, the Midnight Marvels, Damian Drake & Spyder Warrior, Grappler 3 and the Wrecking Crew, Kate Carney, Kassius Koonz, and so many more wrestlers, managers, and talent!
